      "comment": "MULITALO (8) finished in the minors last time when third (22.60) at this track making it two minors from two runs. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. Tough to beat if runs up to recent form. STILTON SPARKLE (7) is a Peter Lagogiane-trained newcomer by Equalizer out of Opulence. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Strong market watch advised but profiles nicely for this. ASPEN RIDGE (3) looked strong on debut March 24 at this track over 388m (22.47) when boxed wide. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Can feature again. BLUE FRECKLE (1) was out of the money here on debut but expected to be much improved.",
